Description: Provides the GenomicInteractions class for handling
    genomic interaction data such as ChIA-PET and Hi-C data.
    Also provides methods for common manipulations and queries
    such as discovery of overlaps in one and two dimensions,
    calculation of bounding boxes, creation of contact matrices 
    and examination of interaction tracks.
biocViews: Software, Infrastructure, DataImport, DataRepresentation, HiC
